Véronique Genest https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/V%C3%A9ronique_Genest 0 Véronique Genest (born Véronique Combouilhaud, 26 June 1956) is a French actress and film producer. She is best known for her starring role as Commissaire Julie Lescaut in the French police drama series Julie Lescaut which ran from 1992 - 2013.
